CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 14, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "Suited For Spring - Models in the fashion revue at May Stern auditorium Monday evening were these charming ladies, who display the latest in spring and summer trends. They are, left to right: Miss Ina Bell Jackson, Mrs. Yola Kemp and Mrs. Cleo Blakney Jones. - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Ina Bell Jackson, Yola Kemp, and Cleo Blakney Jones wearing suits and hats, posed in interior with striped wallpaper
